				<div class="hvres-meaning small">• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/Chu-Tam-T%E1%BB%89nh/%C4%90oan-ng%E1%BB%8D-trung-t%C3%A1c/poem-X0a3R7U8_k6UH67KWORpPw">Đoan ngọ trung tác - 端午中作</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/Chu-Tam-T%E1%BB%89nh/author-xIP2dSGtSWlBkAiuYdG5-g">Chu Tam Tỉnh</a>)<br>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/H%E1%BB%A9a-%C4%90%C6%B0%E1%BB%9Dng/%C4%90%E1%BB%99ng-%C4%90%C3%ACnh-h%E1%BB%93/poem-9oa8qgwccXMTPoNxMBJJ4g">Động Đình hồ - 洞庭湖</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/H%E1%BB%A9a-%C4%90%C6%B0%E1%BB%9Dng/author-TyCkmQcxkIaagTD8FflJDQ">Hứa Đường</a>)<br>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/Nguy%E1%BB%85n-C%C6%B0-Trinh/Kim-D%E1%BB%B1-lan-%C4%91%C3%A0o/poem-MSCD2FdREHsH_gI7coWlWA">Kim Dự lan đào - 金嶼攔濤</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/Nguy%E1%BB%85n-C%C6%B0-Trinh/author-t4xvjEQCpJQuGs7GtUeU9A">Nguyễn Cư Trinh</a>)<br>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/Tr%C6%B0%C6%A1ng-Nguy%C3%AAn-C%C3%A1n/M%C3%A3n-giang-h%E1%BB%93ng-T%E1%BB%B1-D%E1%BB%B1-Ch%C6%B0%C6%A1ng-tr%E1%BB%9F-phong-Ng%C3%B4-Th%C3%A0nh-s%C6%A1n-t%C3%A1c/poem-rpw_feWBqErNK10ng1Jotg">Mãn giang hồng - Tự Dự Chương trở phong Ngô Thành sơn tác - 滿江紅－自豫章阻風吳城山作</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/Tr%C6%B0%C6%A1ng-Nguy%C3%AAn-C%C3%A1n/author-XtDwgc81LrI5SWqmLkXQ1Q">Trương Nguyên Cán</a>)<br>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/%C3%81n-Th%C3%B9/S%C6%A1n-%C4%91%C3%ACnh-li%E1%BB%85u-T%E1%BA%B7ng-ca-n%E1%BB%AF/poem-NKrCsk62l0nMe6MkPHNZTg">Sơn đình liễu - Tặng ca nữ - 山亭柳－贈歌女</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/%C3%81n-Th%C3%B9/author-vOEpptlMHWVC0_k_NsTzRg">Án Thù</a>)<br>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/Khuy%E1%BA%BFt-danh-Trung-Qu%E1%BB%91c/T%C3%A2y-giang-nguy%E1%BB%87t-%C4%90%C4%83ng-th%C3%A0nh-v%C3%A3n-v%E1%BB%8Dng/poem-xi1fp0pkIevHUfUv2TXQdA">Tây giang nguyệt - Đăng thành vãn vọng - 西江月－登城晚望</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/Khuy%E1%BA%BFt-danh-Trung-Qu%E1%BB%91c/author-7Jx-9zMDy2CyYi7fIk3zRA">Khuyết danh Trung Quốc</a>)<br>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/Cao-T%E1%BB%B1-Thanh/Thu-v%C3%A3n/poem-xw7w73rt-Z69DSvWAmiaIw">Thu vãn - 秋晚</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/Cao-T%E1%BB%B1-Thanh/author-wQICzKRVau8PqmJ28C9K6g">Cao Tự Thanh</a>)<br>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/Kh%E1%BA%A3-M%C3%A2n/V%C3%B4-%C4%91%E1%BB%81-V/poem-9Lj_Z8A-VdwVeRG-X0epNQ">Vô đề (V) - 無題</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/Kh%E1%BA%A3-M%C3%A2n/author-bg2Iw4F0Q1WB-Vf8_0Kqcw">Khả Mân</a>)<br>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/%C4%90%E1%BB%97-Ph%E1%BB%A7/V%C5%A9-k%E1%BB%B3-1-Thanh-s%C6%A1n-%C4%91%E1%BA%A1m-v%C3%B4-t%C6%B0/poem-j8vLZEmWAJwFoFzd1YoGgQ">Vũ kỳ 1 (Thanh sơn đạm vô tư) - 雨其一（青山淡無姿）</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/%C4%90%E1%BB%97-Ph%E1%BB%A7/author-Se3x2jWTezvoDpkpSU9qjg">Đỗ Phủ</a>)<br>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/Cao-B%C3%A1-Qu%C3%A1t/V%C5%A9-trung-%C4%91%E1%BB%99-Linh-giang/poem-QkniwJWz6rNwFGS5amteAQ">Vũ trung độ Linh giang - 雨中渡泠江</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/Cao-B%C3%A1-Qu%C3%A1t/author-2eyz08Vw3mwjAHFJik43sA">Cao Bá Quát</a>)<br></div>	</div>
